OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1774026671
OL,3,CTeenage boy dies after flat fire
OL,5,FA teenage boy has died after a flat
OL,6,Ffire in South London.
OL,8,FFour fire engines and around 25
OL,9,Ffirefighters were called to the flat
OL,10,Fon Cooper Road in Southwark.
OL,12,FThe first call came in at 14:57 and
OL,13,Fthe fire was under control by 16:34.
OL,15,FOne boy left before they arrived and
OL,16,Fwas taken to hospital by the London
OL,17,FAmbulance Service.
OL,19,FAnother teenager was declared dead at
OL,20,Fthe scene.
