OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1774026671
OL,3,CTeenage boy dies after flat fire
OL,5,FA London Ambulance Service
OL,6,Fspokesperson said:
OL,8,F"We sent resources to the scene
OL,9,Fincluding ambulance crews, an advanced
OL,10,Fparamedic, an incident response
OL,11,Fofficer and paramedics from our
OL,12,Fhazardous area response team (HART).
OL,14,F"We also dispatched a trauma team in a
OL,15,Fcar from London's Air Ambulance.
OL,17,F"We treated two people. Very sadly,
OL,18,Fdespite the best efforts of our crews,
OL,19,Fa teenager was pronounced dead at the
OL,20,Fscene.
