OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1774026671
OL,3,CTeenage boy dies after flat fire
OL,5,F"We took the other patient to a London
OL,6,Fmajor trauma centre as a priority."
OL,8,FThe incident took place around the
OL,9,Fcorner from Old Kent Road fire station
OL,10,Fbut all the firefighters had
OL,11,Freportedly been dispatched to another
OL,12,Fsituation in Tulse Hill.
OL,14,FThis resulted in callouts from across
OL,15,Fthe area- with crews from Dockhead,
OL,16,FDowgate, Shadwell and Whitechapel fire
OL,17,Fstations being deployed.
OL,19,FThe cause of the fire is being
OL,20,Finvestigated.
